==============================================================================
Release 0.01 of CGI::Untaint::isbn
==============================================================================

NAME

  CGI::Untaint::isbn - validate an isbn

SYNOPSIS

  use CGI::Untaint;
  my $handler = CGI::Untaint->new($q->Vars);

  my $isbn = $handler->extract(-as_isbn => 'isbn');

INSTALLATION

  perl Makefile.pl
  make
  make test
  make install

